channel.title: I need help with port forwarding my rs p server
channel.description:
Hi, i need help portfowarding, heres information about my router.
D-Link DSLG604t. I use wireless btw.
I don't know where to find a guide for portfowarding with wireless internet. I searched the different kinds of modems for wireless. I can't seem to find D-Link DSLG604t. please help me, my friends want to play my server badly
